WEBVTT

00:00:00.413 --> 00:00:03.791
(Clip) Crowd: LA Rams! LA Rams! LA Rams!

00:00:04.357 --> 00:00:08.222
Adam Grant: 2016 was supposed to be
a good year in the NFL for the Rams.

00:00:08.929 --> 00:00:11.729
They were relocating back
from Saint Louis to Los Angeles.

00:00:12.099 --> 00:00:13.305
A fresh start.

00:00:13.329 --> 00:00:14.479
A new home.

00:00:14.980 --> 00:00:17.982
But they only won four games, and lost 12.

00:00:18.567 --> 00:00:19.717
They stank.

00:00:20.107 --> 00:00:23.074
And they hadn't had
a winning season in 14 years.

00:00:24.147 --> 00:00:27.563
But the next year, 2017,
things were different.

